    <item>
      <title>阿根廷请求解除伯福德扣押资产的意图</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/argentina-requests-relief-from-burford-s-intent-to-seize-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷已要求曼哈顿法院阻止伯福德资本立即试图扣押其外国资产，因为该对冲基金试图收回法官裁定其欠阿根廷欠下的数十亿美元资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/argentina-requests-relief-from-burford-s-intent-to-seize-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 19:56:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
