    </item>
    <item>
      <title>毒枭越狱后厄瓜多尔诺博阿宣布进入紧急状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/drug-lord-s-escape-adds-to-pressure-on-ecuador-s-new-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔最臭名昭著的毒枭之一越狱，安第斯国家其他监狱再次爆发骚乱后，总统丹尼尔·诺博亚周一宣布进入为期 60 天的紧急状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/drug-lord-s-escape-adds-to-pressure-on-ecuador-s-new-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 17:03:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着胡塞武装威胁加剧，中远集团将停止预订前往以色列的船舶</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/cosco-to-stop-booking-ships-into-israel-as-houthi-threats-spiral</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于胡塞武装分子对在以色列航行的船只进行威胁和袭击，集装箱运输巨头中国远洋海运集团公司将停止向以色列运送货物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/cosco-to-stop-booking-ships-into-israel-as-houthi-threats-spiral</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 10:17:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官员称，以色列空袭炸死黎巴嫩真主党高级指挥官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-08/palestinians-flee-from-central-gaza-s-main-hospital-as-fighting-draws-closer-and-aid-groups-withdraw</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝鲁特（美联社）——以色列周一在黎巴嫩南部发动空袭，炸死了一名真主党精锐指挥官，这是越境交锋不断升级的最新一起，引发了人们对另一场中东战争的担忧，尽管加沙的战斗造成了越来越多的平民伤亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-08/palestinians-flee-from-central-gaza-s-main-hospital-as-fighting-draws-closer-and-aid-groups-withdraw</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 09:18:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>劳伦·博伯特否认在餐厅殴打前夫；警方发射探测器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-07/officers-in-colorado-are-investigating-an-apparent-altercation-between-rep-boebert-and-ex-husband</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科罗拉多州 SILT（美联社）科罗拉多州锡尔特市警方周日证实，正在对美国众议员劳伦·博伯特和前夫杰森·博伯特在一家餐厅发生的明显争吵进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-07/officers-in-colorado-are-investigating-an-apparent-altercation-between-rep-boebert-and-ex-husband</guid>
